channel.title: Router Help! Problem!
channel.description:
ok i got my router from sky broadband.
i have 2 computers connected to the router and 2 laptops
i have been trying to port forward for a long time. i enter the ip in and enter what should be admin/password or 1234, i click ok and it just prompts me again for the username and pass? wtf?
my router is netgear dg834gt. no one has changed the router's user and pass!
what is wrong?
i dont want to use hamachi because no one ever comes on my server.
help me please. i really want to run it on normal.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 03, 2008, 04:54:39 PM[/size][hr]help me[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 03, 2008, 05:00:05 PM[/size][hr].
